{
  "stem": "15938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my father overheard it, and he came into the room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I only just realized the significance of it-- how wrong-- how bad it was that we never believed it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father said, I don't want you to tell these stories for my children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then when the girls left the room, he said, don't listen because they are completely mad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "These things can't happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's an imagination.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The next day, we looked at this girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "How dare they tell us these stories.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So just to show how things were happening literally a few miles away, and we didn't know, and we didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He didn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He did not believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody believed it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody believed it there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody moved.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There wasn't a person who left our town from being frightened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was this attitude it can't happen to me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it's only over the borders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It can never come over the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I think that is a human-- you don't want to believe it because-- and if you believe it, what will you do?",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't like in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a transport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could go.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, we couldn't-- there was nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But maybe if you would have believed it, we would have made a bigger effort.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just did not believe it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they heard about the Nazi party, but they didn't know it was that bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Once they came in, once they invaded our town, we knew it was bad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But not that bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, going to Auschwitz wasn't-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] even on the way to Auschwitz, we wouldn't believe, you know, what was happening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I don't know if it's human nature which makes you not believe or-- or really we didn't believe.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
